Class MainActivity

      • edu.mills.cs180a.classlist.MainActivity

  • public class MainActivity
extends Activity
    An Activity that displays a list of the names and pictures of people in CS 180A. If a name is clicked on, a box pops up asking what app the user would like to use to send an email, and creates an email with that person's email address in the to send field.
